                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/819.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Consul at Puerto Plata</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams—Paraphrases.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Puerto Plata</hi>
                        </placeName>, <lb/>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-04-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 1, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Arias yesterday agreed with Vasquez here to resist election of Velásquez. Cibao
                    apparently united to make war in case of election of Velasquez.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hathaway</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
